article.description: — Keenon Cole put up 42 points as Lindenwood beat Southeast Missouri State 74-68 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Cole scores 42, Lindenwood takes down Southeast Missouri State 74-68
article.linkText: Cole scores 42, Lindenwood takes down Southeast Missouri State 74-68
article.story: CAPE GIRARDEAU, Mo. -- — Keenon Cole put up 42 points as Lindenwood beat Southeast Missouri State 74-68 on Thursday night. Cole also contributed 11 rebounds for the Lions (7-9, 1-2 Ohio Valley Conference). Darius Beane scored 20 points while going 9 of 15 and 2 of 4 from the free throw line, and added five rebounds. Josh Earley led the Redhawks (6-11, 1-3) in scoring, finishing with 16 points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
